#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.4:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Bhaṇḍagāmavagga"
msgstr "1. At Bhaṇḍa Village"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Dutiyakhatasutta"
msgstr "4. Broken (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.4:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Catūsu, bhikkhave, micchā paṭipajjamāno bālo abyatto asappuriso khataṃ "
"upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca "
"apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"“When a foolish, incompetent bad person acts wrongly toward four people they "
"keep themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and criticized "
"by sensible people, and they make much bad karma."

msgctxt "an4.4:1.2"
msgid "Katamesu catūsu?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"Mātari, bhikkhave, micchā paṭipajjamāno bālo abyatto asappuriso khataṃ "
"upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca "
"apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr "Mother …"

msgctxt "an4.4:1.4"
msgid ""
"Pitari, bhikkhave, micchā paṭipajjamāno … pe … tathāgate, bhikkhave, micchā "
"paṭipajjamāno … pe … tathāgatasāvake, bhikkhave, micchā paṭipajjamāno bālo "
"abyatto asappuriso khataṃ upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti "
"sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr "father … a Realized One … and a disciple of a Realized One."

msgctxt "an4.4:1.5"
msgid ""
"Imesu kho, bhikkhave, catūsu micchā paṭipajjamāno bālo abyatto asappuriso "
"khataṃ upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"When a foolish, incompetent bad person acts wrongly toward these four people "
"they keep themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and "
"criticized by sensible people, and they make much bad karma."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.4:2.1"
msgid ""
"Catūsu, bhikkhave, sammā paṭipajjamāno paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ "
"anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca puññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent good person acts rightly toward four people they "
"keep themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and "
"criticized by sensible people, and they make much merit."

msgctxt "an4.4:2.2"
msgid "Katamesu catūsu?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.4:2.3"
msgid ""
"Mātari, bhikkhave, sammā paṭipajjamāno paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ "
"anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca puññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr "Mother …"

msgctxt "an4.4:2.4"
msgid ""
"Pitari, bhikkhave, sammā paṭipajjamāno … pe … tathāgate, bhikkhave, sammā "
"paṭipajjamāno … pe … tathāgatasāvake, bhikkhave, sammā paṭipajjamāno paṇḍito "
"viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti "
"ananuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca puññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr "father … a Realized One … and a disciple of a Realized One."

msgctxt "an4.4:2.5"
msgid ""
"Imesu kho, bhikkhave, catūsu sammā paṭipajjamāno paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso "
"akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca "
"viññūnaṃ, bahuñca puññaṃ pasavatīti."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent good person acts rightly toward these four people "
"they keep themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and "
"criticized by sensible people, and they make much merit."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.5"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.4:3.1"
msgid "Mātari pitari cāpi,"
msgstr "A person who does wrong"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:3.2"
msgid "yo micchā paṭipajjati;"
msgstr "by their mother or father,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:3.3"
msgid "Tathāgate vā sambuddhe,"
msgstr "or a Realized One, a Buddha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:3.4"
msgid "atha vā tassa sāvake;"
msgstr "or one of their disciples,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:3.5"
msgid "Bahuñca so pasavati,"
msgstr "makes much bad karma."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:3.6"
msgid "apuññaṃ tādiso naro."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: Tāya naṃ adhammacariyāya → tāya adhammacariyāya (bj, s1-3, km) | tāya adhammacāriyāya (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.4:4.1"
msgid "Tāya naṃ adhammacariyāya,"
msgstr "Because of their unprincipled conduct"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:4.2"
msgid "Mātāpitūsu paṇḍitā;"
msgstr "toward their parents,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:4.3"
msgid "Idheva naṃ garahanti,"
msgstr "they’re criticized in this life by the astute,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:4.4"
msgid "Peccāpāyañca gacchati."
msgstr "and they depart to be reborn in a place of loss."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.4:5.1"
msgid "Mātari pitari cāpi,"
msgstr "A person who does right"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:5.2"
msgid "yo sammā paṭipajjati;"
msgstr "by their mother and father,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:5.3"
msgid "Tathāgate vā sambuddhe,"
msgstr "or a Realized One, a Buddha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:5.4"
msgid "atha vā tassa sāvake;"
msgstr "or one of their disciples,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:5.5"
msgid "Bahuñca so pasavati,"
msgstr "makes much merit."

#. <br>
#. VAR: puññaṃ etādiso → puññampi tādiso (bj, km) | puññaṃpi tādiso (s1-3)
msgctxt "an4.4:5.6"
msgid "puññaṃ etādiso naro."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.4:6.1"
msgid "Tāya naṃ dhammacariyāya,"
msgstr "Because of their principled conduct"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.4:6.2"
msgid "mātāpitūsu paṇḍitā;"
msgstr "toward their parents,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: Idheva → idha ceva (bj)
msgctxt "an4.4:6.3"
msgid "Idheva naṃ pasaṃsanti,"
msgstr "they’re praised in this life by the astute,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: sagge pamodatī”ti → sagge ca modatīti (bj) | sagge pamodantīti (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.4:6.4"
msgid "pecca sagge pamodatī”ti."
msgstr "and they depart to rejoice in heaven.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.4:6.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
